title: Birth Stories & Camo's New Man
description:
On this week's episode, Camo dishes about his new relationship and Tasia rants about brands constantly trying to take advantage of influencers. Together they answer your fan submitted questions from Tasia's kids' birth stories and how their friendships have changed over the years. Tune in to catch up with the ever evolving dynamic duo!
